#: src/alfred/supervisor/core.py:227
msgid "supervisor.start.already_started"
msgstr ""
"Supervisor.start() called twice without an intervening stop(). The "
"supervisor is single-instance per process; re-entrancy would orphan the "
"first TaskGroup."

#: src/alfred/supervisor/core.py:439
